<L>__{exterior street morning}
<A>__{hector and lucinnius are approaching the home of cyprian. hector as usual is walking some paces behind his master, and he carries a large satchel of documents. cyprian's home is a street palace. it is early in the morning, but there is already activity around the house, visitors coming and going, messengers, petitioners. a few impor tant callers arrive in litters, carried by slaves. lucinnius and hector even have to join a line at the door and are checked in by the gateman. lucinnius's hopes of quietly bending cyprian's ear are dashed. it seems as if the whole world owes allegiance to this provincial mr. big.}
